Happy International Women’s Day! 

Words cannot express how grateful and excited I am to share my collaboration with the incredible Bisa Butler and National Geographic 📸 @natgeo @bisabutler 

In advance of Women’s History Month I had the pleasure of visiting Bisa’s studio to learn more about her artistic process and create a portrait of her. Bisa currently has a solo exhibition at The Gordon Parks Foundation running through April 14. You can see more of her work here @bisabutler @gordonparksfoundation

On Friday I married the most wonderful, kind, talented and angelic man. Words cannot express my love and gratitude for you and I cannot wait for our wedding celebrations to continue this summer.

It was so special to have this impromptu city hall celebration with both of our families and some of my closest and most wonderful friends. Thank you all for supporting us, we love you all so much. 

The photography was a Herculean group effort by @spyderman31 @pia_peterson  @schuylersloman and #meredithlawder. I hate being photographed so thank you all for making images that have brought me so much joy ❤️

👰🏻‍♀️👰🏻‍♂️
